title: Google Assistant not working. No squeeze/audio cue. Can't even open/access settings.
content: Assistant doesn't work. No swipe left to "cards" screen. The search bar at the bottom will only search apps instead of web search. I went to play store and it showed the app as not installed, so I reinstalled it. Still nothing. When I try to access assistant in settings, it just goes to home screen now. WTF?
category: Google Assistant and Voice Actions, Google Pixel 3 XL
